			<div class="dablink">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Tom_Nagel" title="Tom Nagel">Tom Nagel</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vcard vevent" cellspacing="5" style="width: 22em; text-align: left; font-size: 88%; line-height: 1.5em;">
<caption class="" style="font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold;">Thomas Nagel</caption>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; background-color:#B0C4DE"><a href="/wiki/Western_Philosophy" title="Western Philosophy" class="mw-redirect">Western Philosophy</a><br />
