<th style="">Main interests</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/Philosophy_of_mind" title="Philosophy of mind">Philosophy of mind</a>, <a href="/wiki/Political_Philosophy" title="Political Philosophy" class="mw-redirect">Political Philosophy</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ethics" title="Ethics">Ethics</a>, <a href="/wiki/Epistemology" title="Epistemology">Epistemology</a></td>
</tr>
