<p><a name="Books" id="Books"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Thomas_Nagel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Books">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Books</span></h3>
