<li>1997, "Assisted Suicide: The Philosophers' Brief" (with R. Dworkin, R. Nozick, J. Rawls, T. Scanlon, and J. J. Thomson), <i>New York Review of Books</i>, March 27, 1997.</li>
<li>1998, "Reductionism and Antireductionism", in <i>The Limits of Reductionism in Biology</i>, Novartis Symposium 213, John Wiley &amp; Sons, pp. 3-10.</li>
