<li>1998, "Conceiving the Impossible and the Mind-Body Problem", <i>Philosophy</i>, vol. 73, no. 285, pp. 337-352. <a href="http://philosophy.fas.nyu.edu/docs/IO/1172/conceiving.pdf" class="external text" title="http://philosophy.fas.nyu.edu/docs/IO/1172/conceiving.pdf" rel="nofollow">Online PDF</a></li>
